"determiners"

"Lexical entries are case sensitive"
the  D *     (^ SPEC PRED) = 'the'
             (^ SPEC DEF) = +.

The  D *  (^ SPEC PRED) = 'the'
          (^ SPEC DEF) = +.
          @(OT-MARK CAPITAL) "for generation disprefer capitalization".

a   D *  (^ SPEC PRED) = 'a'
         (^ SPEC DEF) = -.


"prepositions"

by 	  P * @(PREP by). 

to 	  P *  @(PREP to);
          PARTinf * (^ VFORM) =c inf.

on 	  P * @(PREP on). 

in 	  P * @(PREP in). 

with 	  P * @(PREP with).

for 	  P * @(PREP for). 


"complementizers"

that C * (^COMP-FORM) = that.


"Coordination"

and  CONJ * @(COORD-FORM %stem);
     CONJnp * @(COORD-FORM %stem) @(NUM pl).

"punctuation"

. PERIOD * (^ STMT-TYPE) = declarative. 

, COMMA  * . 

!  EXCL * (^ STMT-TYPE) = exclamation. 


